I_a,A \in M_n
 I_b, B \in M_m
 e^{A \otimes I_b +I_a \otimes B} = e^A \otimes e^B~
f
f(A\otimes I_b) = f(A)\otimes I_b~~~~\text{and}~~~  f(I_b \otimes A) = I_b \otimes f(A)~.
